6995309101339e-14, \"text\": \"AO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999947777266635, \"rank\": 3.114880142936266e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 267, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Paralympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympics GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Paralympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Paralympic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kay, alongside Emma Willis, will give insights into the lives of our Olympic stars through interviews and appearances by athletes both legendary and up-and-coming.\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Willis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Willis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Willis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Willis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The extravaganza, also featuring performances from Clean Bandit, Jess Glynne, Pete Tong and Rag'n'Bone Man, will be broadcast on BBC One and iPlayer the following day.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clean_Bandit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clean Bandit\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clean_Bandit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clean_Bandit\"}, {\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Glynne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jess Glynne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Glynne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Glynne\"}, {\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pete Tong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4209739192088117e-16, \"text\": \"BBC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}, {\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vernon\\u00a0said: \\\"I have seen first-hand how amazingly dedicated and talented our athletes are and the difference the support of National Lottery players makes to their ability to be the best they can be.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9935806516819926, \"rank\": 0.006399576570720567, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The National Lottery's Team GB Homecoming event will be a moment to recognise the achievements of the athletes, and thank National Lottery players who have helped them on their journey to Paris.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 986, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9935806516819926, \"rank\": 0.006399576570720567, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}, {\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999222916388, \"rank\": 7.770837094386359e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not wait to celebrate together!\\\"\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another celebration by The National Lottery, the Paralympics GB Homecoming, will be held at the Utilita Arena, Birmingham on Thursday, September 12.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_(United_Kingdom)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The National Lottery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_(United_Kingdom)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_(United_Kingdom)\"}, {\"begin\": 1212, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"score\": 0.9999995034587623, \"rank\": 4.958812517997079e-07, \"text\": \"Birmingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes' jubilant return home is a show of gratitude to National Lottery players, whose support plays a crucial part in our athletes' successes.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1312,